				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Load act 2, teleport to Wulbren (he's in the prison in Moonrise). Speak to wulbren and persuade him you're here to help - he'll ask you to get 'tools'. Throw him something he can't use (like a dagger or shovel) and these will trigger. "
				},
